ivardefs.name: allDay
ivardefs.desc: Is this always available? (hence times are irrelevant) e.g. 24 hour service.

ivardefs.name: availableEndTime
ivardefs.desc: The closing time of day. Note: If the AllDay flag is set, then this time is ignored.

ivardefs.name: availableStartTime
ivardefs.desc: The opening time of day. Note: If the AllDay flag is set, then this time is ignored.

ivardefs.name: daysOfWeek_
ivardefs.desc: Indicates which days of the week are available between the start and end Times.

properties.desc: A collection of times that the Service Site is available.
